How to see documentation:
----------------------------

1. Install dependencies: Doxygen, Roffit
$ sudo apt-get install doxygen roffit

2. Run configure
$ ./configure
Note: If you configure script is not present in top directory run autoconf and then configure again

3. Build documentation
$ make doc 

NOTE: For detailed description on compiling zipgateway please refer to documentation
----  created after step 4.

4. Open src/doc/html/index.hml in browser
$ xdg-open src/doc/html/index.html
